CheckersPlayerInterface
public class HAL900S
extends HAL900
implements CheckersPlayerInterface

The HAL900S is an advanced Artificial Intelligence for Checkers. It uses a depth-limited search and a mini-max algorithm with alpha-beta pruning. The HAL900S is a reduced version of the HAL900 that moves within a few seconds.

Version:
"1.15 - 16 August 2008"
Author:
